    "# VisionAid Master Benchmark — 22 Classes (SAHI + Negatives)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Strategic ordered steps:**\n",
    "1. **Dataset Rectification** (COCO Injection + YOLO-World Auto-labeling)\n",
    "2. **Training Benchmark** (n, s variants at 832px)\n",
    "3. **Validation with SAHI** (Sliced Inference for small object recall)\n",
    "4. **Negative Sample Accuracy** (Reducing false alerts)"
   ]
  },
